{"tid":2260054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14歲少年被指3月8日將雪糕筒拋出路面 今獲撤控守行為處理","createTime":"2020-10-27T09:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T11:07:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"86322b8749dfb6651d69a95962e89e70315e971a","tid":2260054,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:38:56.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎年初開始肆虐，今年3月有市民反對政府將大埔賽馬會普通科門診診所列為指定診所，同月8日在區內發起遊行，惟遭警方腰斬驅散。當日下午約4時，警方發現一名14歲少年在安祥路交通燈下，將雪糕筒拋出路面，途經車輛需避開。警方將少年拘捕，控以一項在公眾地方造成阻礙罪。案件今於粉嶺法院少年庭再訊時，控方同意撤控，改以簽保守行為處理。<br />\n<br />\n根據少年同意的案情指，當日他被捕時，警方在其背包內發現寫有「光復香港，時代革命」旗幟及桿枝，少年警誡下保持緘默。少年今獲准自簽2,000元、1守行為兩年，控方撤回原有控罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/EJKIXFX5KZFBBKMMI6QCLXIEVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FEJKIXFX5KZFBBKMMI6QCLXIEVI%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDCUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=8805c363\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FEJKIXFX5KZFBBKMMI6QCLXIEVI%2F&h=06c50a5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/EJKIXFX5KZFBBKMMI6QCLXIEVI/</a>"},{"pid":"0a2cbd1a3b6d62002681d4526c64498784ee5272","tid":2260054,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c977c8c9eac40d2806877d777770bc965ada1a59","tid":2260054,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:44:11.000Z","msg":"點解撤左控佢仲有權叫佢守行為?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c653846f14815ab5e32816546e0588a9049bb5d","tid":2260054,"uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c977c8c9eac40d280687